These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, skateboard, tram
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the mexican is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the fan of techno##2
10. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the rat##1
11. the fan of funk is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | skateboard  | jet-ski    | tram    | bike   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

