.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, scooter, bike
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
 2. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the colombian##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the colombian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the mexican is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Transport         | scooter | bike | skateboard   | tram |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian   | indian   | spanish    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

