 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 5. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of gospel is between the german and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of folk is the blend-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is the blend-smoker##1
 9. the colombian is on the far right##1
10. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | iced-tea    | 7up       | tea       |
| Cigar          | baccarat    | blend | havana | oliveros     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | folk        | gospel    | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | german      | indian    | colombian |

